00:47:01,131 --> 00:47:04,011
We're going to move to Q&A. But before we do, give me a

811
00:47:04,151 --> 00:47:05,832
round of applause for all the people that worked on

812
00:47:05,852 --> 00:47:06,532
Command & Conquer.

813
00:47:06,552 --> 00:47:07,612
So they hear this.

814
00:47:24,156 --> 00:47:24,437
Thank you.

