00:51:24,258 --> 00:51:28,201
But once the team started really deviating the products

900
00:51:28,261 --> 00:51:29,982
and they were clearly distinctive,

901
00:51:30,623 --> 00:51:32,204
I always found that it was really inspiring.

902
00:51:32,764 --> 00:51:34,225
And having another company out there

903
00:51:34,245 --> 00:51:35,686
that was trying to one-up the game.

